# id pqawasqpijhcdhec
* if people individually have right to something then they have right to it together too, they are free to do it cooperatively too
* constraining the cooperative usages of rights is a form of constraining the rights themselves
* it is bad, it should not happen, people should have the rights to use their rights cooperatively; hence organizations should have the same rights as individuals
* people are often much stronger together in an organization then separately; hence tyrannical oppression is much easier of free organization is oppressed; that is why tyrants always are against the freedom of organizations of people and constraining the freedom of organizations is always tyrannical
